729762f-c.title: Richmond: Tompkins Avenue - School Road
729762f-c.text:
Tompkins avenue, at School Road, showing road construction and the erection of a foot walk across the railroad tracks. The view is north along Tompkins Avenue, the tracks crossing the latter
driectly above School Road.
August 23, 1935
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, viewing alOng the east side of Tompkins
Avenue. The 2-story house lright) is at the N.E. corner of
the two thoroughfares.
August 23, 1935
P. L. Sperr
(3)
Viewing north along the new and old (left)railroad
tracks. Note Tompkins Avenue crossing the tracks from the right
fore- to the left background of the picture.
August 23, 1935
P. L. Sperr
